    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nMost other Python software conform to XDG so I think Cython should too.\r\n\r\n### Code to reproduce the behaviour:\r\n```\r\nfrom Cython.Utils import get_cython_cache_dir\r\nget_cython_cache_dir()\r\n'/home/bjourne/.cython'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nget_cython_cache_dir() should return `~/.cache/cython`.\r\n\r\n### OS\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Python version\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Cython version\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
