            "body": "`~/.cache/cython` should be used when XDG_CACHE_HOME is not set: $XDG_CACHE_HOME defines the base directory relative to which user-specific non-essential data files should be stored. If $XDG_CACHE_HOME is either not set or empty, a default equal to $HOME/.cache should be used. ",
